main event: A photo of an unidentified object was observed in Pretoria, South Africa on July 23, 1956.
interesting points: The object was observed for 10 minutes.
The object was described as similar to a light fixture or larger monitor/satellite.
No photographs were taken of the observed object.
The sighting occurred at 2359 I.R. (time not specified).
The type of observation was ground-visual.
